{"tid":263964,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)水銀蒸發令 陰兒房/兒凶1-3","createTime":"2017-05-30T12:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T18:32:09.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ea1e95a51763827c9ebbd9b87f48cd6098c078be","tid":263964,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:33:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2F&d=e3vSqkJZa08LwYwIKWn%2FMzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=6f16013c\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=e3vSqkJZa08LwYwIKWn%2FMzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=1833ad56\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=e3vSqkJZa08LwYwIKWn%2FMzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=7508b6cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a8/Mercuryrisingposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa8%2FMercuryrisingposter.jpg&h=baba1724&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/d4/Insidious_%E2%80%93_Chapter_2_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fd4%2FInsidious_%25E2%2580%2593_Chapter_2_Poster.jpg&h=d2b85099&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.FBI調查員艾特&middot;傑菲（布魯斯&middot;威利飾演）一次奉派調查一起父母離奇遇害，男孩失蹤的案子，當傑菲前往現場查案時，發現這名有自閉症狀的男孩賽門因為父母被殺害而驚嚇過度，無法言語，他歷經的痛苦引起傑菲的共鳴，而且直覺認為他身陷極大危險，於是要求警方為他提供保護。當警方無故撒退，傑菲就帶著賽門逃命<br />\n<br />\n2.蕊娜(Renai)與喬許(Josh Lambert)與三個小孩搬到一間新房子。有一天兒子發生意外並從此昏迷不醒，之後家裡便發生許多神秘事件，不得不請靈媒過來解決。<br />\n<br />\n3.故事緊隨前集，在小男孩被成功救出但父親卻被惡靈附體後，Lambert一家的惡夢才真正展開，背後的真相也逐漸浮出水面。<br />\n<br />\n4.本集的導演由溫子仁長期編劇夥伴雷沃納爾親自操刀，雷過去曾擔任奪魂鋸及陰兒房系列電影編劇。前２集創下全美票房佳績的續集電影，這一集將故事拉到恐怖的源頭，早在蘭柏特一家鬧鬼之前，一切的神祕鬼怪開始於一個青少女及她的家庭&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n9 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a1d8432aaaf610f487d056954d7fd134bbb949","tid":263964,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ecb5ac96375792a991cdc8f13444bc48ffee80a","tid":263964,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T13:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da0a041dae8440a65fe89d1fd7940f9e5d37978","tid":263964,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T13:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba68181004f463e12ded3507986609f8d3eb0de1","tid":263964,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:52:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef33efad51a052fbe8f601dd13a1b1739a60f9b7","tid":263964,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T15:33:58.000Z","msg":"<i